import {configureStore} from '@reduxjs/toolkit'
import reducer from '../Reducers'

const initialState =  {
    lister: [],
    deck: {main: [], extra: []},
    isLoading: false,
    hasMoreItemsToLoad: false,
    nextPageToLoad: ''
}

const store = configureStore({
    reducer: reducer,
    preloadedState: initialState,
})

export default store
